<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lỗi Server - 500</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@3.5.0/fonts/remixicon.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .error-animation {
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
            40% {
                transform: translateY(-30px);
            }
            60% {
                transform: translateY(-15px);
            }
        }
        .gradient-bg {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="gradient-bg min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="max-w-md w-full mx-4">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-8 text-center">
            <!-- Error Icon -->
            <div class="error-animation mb-6">
                <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto">
                    <i class="ri-error-warning-line text-red-500 text-4xl"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Error Title -->
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Lỗi Server 500</h1>
            
            <!-- Error Message -->
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Xin lỗi, đã xảy ra lỗi nội bộ server. Chúng tôi đang khắc phục sự cố này.
            </p>
            
            <!-- Error Details (if available) -->
            <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined' && error) { %>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6 text-left">
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2">Chi tiết lỗi:</h3>
                    <code class="text-xs text-red-600 break-all"><%= error %></code>
                </div>
            <% } %>
            
            <!-- Action Buttons -->
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <button onclick="window.history.back()" 
                        class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="ri-arrow-left-line mr-2"></i>
                    Quay lại
                </button>
                
                <a href="/" 
                   class="w-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="ri-home-line mr-2"></i>
                    Về trang chủ
                </a>
                
                <% if (typeof isAuthenticated !== 'undefined' && isAuthenticated) { %>
                    <a href="/admin/dashboard" 
                       class="w-full bg-green-100 text-green-700 py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-200 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center">
                        <i class="ri-dashboard-line mr-2"></i>
                        Admin Dashboard
                    </a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Help Text -->
            <div class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-500">
                <p>Nếu lỗi vẫn tiếp tục xảy ra, vui lòng liên hệ với chúng tôi.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="text-center mt-6">
            <p class="text-white text-sm">
                © 2024 Shop Admin. Tất cả quyền được bảo lưu.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
